title: Molly Moo Cow And The Indians ( Van Beuren 1935)

sources.title: Molly Moo Cow And The Indians ( Van Beuren 1935)
sources.description: A Conestoga Wagon leads Molly Moo-Cow and some ducks through the hills. The ducks stop for a swim by a tepee and go to explore the settlement. Molly misses her friends and goes to look for them; when she finds them she discovers they're behaving like Native Americans, and she joins in.
